reviewText: Great series. Eastmans started it all. I remember go to his grandpa show in Spokane when it all started
Excellent representation of fair chase hunting
Great show! Not only in production quality but showing the ethical side of hunters on public land. Cant wait for more shows!
I can't wait until Eastmans' releases more seasons of the TV show on Amazon Prime!
Great show that is fun and educational. Ethical hunters showing great respect for wildlife and conservation

I just received this dvd and I enjoy it very much. It will be a keeper. I like to get hunting dvd's out every so often especially in the off season as I plan for next years hunt. This will be watched several times in the future.
